02:53.373 --> 02:56.276 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANGEL COLON, Orlando Attack
Survivor: I hear
him, and he's shooting everyone
that's already

02:56.309 --> 03:02.382 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
