these kinds of events are going
to keep on

04:12.919 --> 04:14.788 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
happening.

04:14.821 --> 04:17.791 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: After the
session with the
president, FBI Director James
Comey also briefed

04:17.824 --> 04:21.761 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
