04:49.756 --> 04:53.293 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DEW SIZEMORE, Florida: And I
feel like I can
leave here and start to heal.
And it's the

04:53.326 --> 04:57.297 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
