10:29.496 --> 10:34.400 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we are now seeing how
dangerous this kind
of mind-set and this kind of
thinking can

10:34.434 --> 10:42.408 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
