presumptive
Republican nominee for president
of the United

10:54.521 --> 11:01.961 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
States to bar all Muslims from
emigrating
into America. We hear language
that singles

11:01.995 --> 11:12.605 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
